Subject: [PATCH v2 3/3] efi_selftest: test unaligned memory access

According to the UEFI spec unaligned memory access should be enabled on
CPUs supporting it.

Signed-off-by: Heinrich Schuchardt <xypron.glpk@gmx.de>
---
